      </div>
      <div class="footer__bottom">
        <p>© 2026 Dubai Coffee Guide. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p><a href="https://techsites.ai" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Powered by TechSites.ai</a></p>
      </div>
